file.name: testopenapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Title
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: http://testapi.com
paths:
  "/all/":
    get:
      summary: List all things
      operationId: listThings
      tags:
        - things
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A paged array of things
          headers:
            x-next:
              description: A link to the next page of responses
              schema:
                type: string
            x-response-id:
              "$ref": "#/components/headers/xResponseId"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Things"
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
    post:
      summary: Create a thing
      operationId: createThings
      tags:
        - things
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Null response
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
  "/things":
    get:
      summary: List all things
      operationId: listThings
      tags:
        - things
      parameters:
        - name: limit
          in: query
          description: How many items to return at one time (max 100)
          required: false
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A paged array of things
          headers:
            x-next:
              description: A link to the next page of responses
              schema:
                type: string
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Things"
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
    post:
      summary: Create a thing
      operationId: createThings
      tags:
        - things
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Null response
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
  "/things/{thingId}":
    get:
      summary: Info for a specific thing
      operationId: showThingById
      tags:
        - things
      parameters:
        - name: thingId
          in: path
          required: true
          description: The id of the thing to retrieve
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Expected response to a valid request
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Things"
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
components:
  headers:
    xResponseId:
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
        format: uuid
      description: Unique response ID
  schemas:
    Thing:
      required:
        - id
        - name
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        name:
          type: string
        tag:
          type: string
    Things:
      type: array
      items:
        "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Thing"
    Error:
      required:
        - code
        - message
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        message:
          type: string

Error: parse: parse spec: parse operations: paths: /things: get: duplicate operationId: "listThings"
